{"title":"Limited Edition Esker Japhy x MRP 4130 Trail Hardtail, So Purple, It’ll Hunt Infinity Stones","link":"https://bikerumor.com/esker-x-mrp-limited-edition-purple-japhy-shredkote-steel-trail-hardtail/","date":1692626400000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_frameset-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Esker x MRP limited edition wild purple cerakote Japhy ShredKote steel trail hardtail, frameset detail\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_frameset-detail.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_frameset-detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_frameset-detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_frameset-detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_frameset-detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_frameset-detail-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_frameset-detail-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Esker Cycles pairs up with MRP for a small batch purple run of the steel Japhy trail hardtail to match MRP’s limited edition 120mm ShredKote Raven fork. Fit for Thanos, this limited edition frame and fork get ceramic coated in “Wild Purple” Cerakote, a lighter and more durable matte finish than conventional paint, prosing to keep this trail-shredding hardtail as fresh as grape soda for many years to come…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Esker x MRP ltd. purple Japhy ShredKote steel trail hardtail</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail.jpg\" alt=\"Esker x MRP limited edition wild purple cerakote Japhy ShredKote steel trail hardtail, detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>all photos c. Esker Cycles</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Esker Cycles’ collaboration with MRP then, is a limited run of Japhy frames to match MRP “ShredKote” forks in Wild Purple. That is to say, the quad-butted &amp; tapered frame 4130 chromoly frame gets the exact same lighter, more impact-resistant Cerakote ceramic finish as the fork.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Want to learn more about the Esker Japhy 29er? It just got <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/esker-portage-dropouts-sram-udh-how-to-add-transmission-hayduke-or-japhy/\" target=\"_blank\">an UDH upgrade</a> a couple of weeks ago. But it’s otherwise the same lovely slack <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/esker-cycles-seeks-hardtail-zen-with-modern-steel-japhy-featuring-room-for-29-x-2-8-tires/\" target=\"_blank\">29+ trail hardtail</a> that Esker introduced a few years back. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>A custom color MRP fork, you say?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_custom-color-MRP-forks.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_custom-color-MRP-forks.jpg\" alt=\"Esker x MRP limited edition wild purple cerakote Japhy ShredKote steel trail hardtail, custom color MRP forks\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_custom-color-MRP-forks.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_custom-color-MRP-forks-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_custom-color-MRP-forks-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_custom-color-MRP-forks-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_custom-color-MRP-forks-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_custom-color-MRP-forks-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_custom-color-MRP-forks-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_custom-color-MRP-forks-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>MRP actually offers 18 custom Cerakote colors in their <a href=\"https://mrpbike.com/pages/custom-forks\" target=\"_blank\">Custom Forks</a> program, so Esker decided to get on the fun in their favorite Wild Purple. Interestingly, the MRP custom program usually doesn’t include the more burly Raven (usually it’s only Ribbons &amp; Baxters). But Esker preferred the slightly heavier, more adjustable (and adjustable to longer travel) Raven with its bigger tire clearance, set up with 120mm of travel.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Esker X MRP Japhy – Pricing, spec &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_teaser.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_teaser.jpg\" alt=\"Esker x MRP limited edition wild purple cerakote Japhy ShredKote steel trail hardtail, teaser\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_teaser.jpg 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_teaser-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_teaser-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_teaser-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_teaser-768x768.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The limited edition <a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/products/japhy-mrp-shredkote\" target=\"_blank\">Wild Purple Esker X MRP Japhy</a> is available in two different build specs. What’s more, each gets the same Cerakote purple frame, in five sizes (S-XXL), and spec’d with the matching ShredKote 120mm MRP Raven fork.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A wireless GX AXS Transmission build will run you $4950 with:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Race Face Alloy Cockpit<br />SRAM Level 4-Piston Brakes (New Gen)<br />SRAM GX Transmission Drivetrain<br />Wolf Tooth Dropper, Lever, Grips, Headset<br />Industry Nine Hydra Enduro S Wheelset<br />Schwalbe Nobby Nic 29 x 2.6 Tires</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_XT-Special-Blend-complete.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_XT-Special-Blend-complete.jpg\" alt=\"Esker x MRP limited edition wild purple cerakote Japhy ShredKote steel trail hardtail, XT Special Blend complete bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_XT-Special-Blend-complete.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_XT-Special-Blend-complete-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_XT-Special-Blend-complete-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_XT-Special-Blend-complete-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_XT-Special-Blend-complete-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_XT-Special-Blend-complete-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Esker-x-MRP-limited-edition-wild-purple-cerakote-Japhy-ShredKote-steel-trail-hardtail_XT-Special-Blend-complete-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A mechanical XT Special Blend build will cost just $3450 with:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Race Face Alloy Cockpit<br />XT 4-Piston Brakes<br />XT 12-Speed Drivetrain<br />SDG Dropper, Lever, Grips<br />Stan’s Flow S2 Wheelset<br />Schwalbe Nobby Nic 29 x 2.6 Tires</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Get yours direct from Esker Cycles or one of their dealer bike shops.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>EskerCycles.com</em></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/esker-x-mrp-limited-edition-purple-japhy-shredkote-steel-trail-hardtail/\">Limited Edition Esker Japhy x MRP 4130 Trail Hardtail, So Purple, It’ll Hunt Infinity Stones</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"28d47be2419a0f1112c9c327021a77d786a1f9a2d132fcfe178bd69c553b63df","category":"Cycling"}